our business strategy our goal is to become a global leader in the development  manufacture and marketing of precision engineered microsurgical instruments  capital equipment and devices for use in vitreoretinal surgery and neurosurgical applications and to grow our product lines in other specialty surgical markets 
our recent combination of the businesses of valley forge and synergetics is a significant component of our strategy toward achieving these goals 
